    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Massive pieces of solid rock comprising the earth's crust, or lithosphere. There are two types of tectonic plates: continental and oceanic. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
